title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from a table containing highlight/map in the attached report (Bug 121682), an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting the data from the table, the expected result is that the data should be exported without any errors or exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Locate the table containing highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Observe the exception being thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
